lead_paragraph: With a late equalizer and an even later game-winning goal, the Winnipeg Jets reminded the playoff-bound Anaheim Ducks they should never get comfortable at this time in the NHL season.

headline.print_headline: Wheeler Gets Winner as Jets Rally to Stun Ducks in OT, 2-1
